sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Administrator
    participant FE as React<br/>AdminHealthPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>SystemHealthView
    participant SER as SystemHealthSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Redis as Redis Server
    participant Celery as Celery Worker

    A->>FE: Navigate to System Health page
    FE->>API: GET /api/system/health/
    API->>DB: Test database connectivity (free_db, premium_db, exclusive_db)
    DB-->>API: DB status OK / Error
    API->>Redis: Test Redis connection
    Redis-->>API: Redis status OK / Error
    API->>Celery: Check Celery worker status
    Celery-->>API: Worker status OK / Error
    API->>API: Collect CPU, memory, disk metrics
    API->>DB: SystemHealth.objects.create(snapshot)
    DB-->>API: Health snapshot saved
    API->>SER: SystemHealthSerializer(health_data)
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {db_status, redis_status, celery_status, cpu, memory, disk}
    FE->>FE: ServiceCard(service) for each service
    FE->>FE: MetricGauge(metric) for each metric
    FE->>FE: getOverallStatus(all_services)
    FE-->>U: Display system health dashboard with service cards
